# Node.js CI/CD Pipeline

## Objective
Automate the build and deployment of a Node.js application using GitHub Actions and Docker.

## Technologies Used
- Node.js
- Express.js
- Docker
- GitHub Actions
- Docker Hub

## Workflow
1. Push code to the `main` branch.
2. GitHub Actions installs dependencies.
3. Builds the Docker image.
4. Logs in to Docker Hub.
5. Pushes the latest image automatically.

